Work fine. Thanks a lot.

DonÂ´t forget to tun off the "automatic update" in program.

Step 1: Replace 'imfc0.dll' in the installation folder.
Step 2: Activate the program and register.
FYI, you can use any name.
Registration code should be in this format:
####-####-####-####
e.g. 0000-0000-0000-0000

TO STOP THIS PROGRAM FROM VALIDATING THE CODE ONLINE:

Download and install ZoneAlarm, it's free but can slow your system.

Go to program control under firewall settings and click advanced.

Uncheck: "Allow certified microsoft programs" and close it.

Install this warez following included instructions.
